                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3155" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0046</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9566 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">世汇贷P2P网络贷款平台：路在何方？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SHIHUIDAI Network P2P Loan Platform: Where is the Way?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">柯金川，王林琳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">世汇贷（北京）电子商务服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">P2P；网络金融；贷款平台；风险; 监管</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">P2P; network finance;loanplatform;financial risk;supervision</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">P2P网贷平台是金融业发展的一种新型模式，它改变了传统银行业一家独大的格局，为个体小额贷款和投资均提供了新的途径。但是由于中国的网贷市场刚刚兴起，尚处于探索期，相关制度还不健全，导致P2P网贷行业存在着很多问题。本案例依照近两年网贷行业出现的问题和一些网贷公司的实例构建了一个网贷平台公司—世汇贷，在其曲折发展的过程中经历了起伏跌宕，尤其是在创办一年多后公司对未来发展方向进行思考：是否应及早将资金交由第三方托管寻求公司转型呢？在本案例中世汇贷公司面临的一系列局面和采取的一系列措施都引人深思。案例主要从P2P网贷平台的公司运作模式、个人投资理财、风险控制以及信用审核等视角来分析目前网贷行业的普遍面临的问题。本案例主要适用于《金融风险管理》、《金融监管》和《公司治理》等课程的辅助案例。希望读者可以通过本案例认识到P2P网贷平台潜在的道德风险、违约风险、法律风险等问题，给P2P网贷行业以及相关的监管机构带来一些思考和启迪。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">P2P network loan platform is a new mode for the development of financial market.  It has changed the dominant pattern of traditional banking industry and offered a new way for the individual small loans and investments. China&#39;s network financial market is just emerging, the related system is still not perfect. It has a long way to go before a mature network business environment is established.This case is developed with a virtual platform --- SHIHUIDAI, in accordance with the examples happened in recent two years network loan finance. Through the ups and downs of the SHIHUIDAI growth experience in the past two years, it gives rise to the critical thinking for SHIHUIDAI future development direction: Whether the funds will be managed by the third party? Whether to seek the company&#39;s transition to the unsecured intermediary? This case analyzes the problems mainly from the perspective of the business model for P2P network loan platform, individual financial investment, risk control and credit checking, which has implicit runoff risk, operational risk and legal risk of network loans. It is hopeful to bring some thinking and inspiration to the P2P network loan platforms and related regulatory agencies. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融风险管理》、《金融监管》、《项目管理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金融风险管理的相关理论；公司治理的相关理论；互联网金融的法律法规</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
